Class JAST

  • java.lang.Object
    • jminusminus.JAST
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JClassDeclaration, JCompilationUnit, JFieldDeclaration, JFormalParameter, JMethodDeclaration, JStatement, JVariableDeclarator
    abstract class JAST
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract superclass of all nodes in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
